      <title>欧佩克供应率和关税动荡的油汇到四年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧佩克+出人意料的产量增加以及全球贸易战的惊人产量增加之后，石油跌至四年低点，这也使商品市场从金属到天然气都震撼了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:53:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街对中国报复的工作不受约束：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票在全球范围内跌落，债券飙升，石油跌至四年的低位，中国加强了与唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易战的斗争，以加强对经济的担忧，尽管有扎实的就业报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧佩克+撞击石油市场，政策转变以推动价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/opec-stuns-oil-market-with-policy-switch-to-drive-down-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在这十年的大部分时间里，欧佩克+联盟一直是全球最坚定的油价后卫。本周仅在片刻之内，这个角色急剧扭转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/opec-stuns-oil-market-with-policy-switch-to-drive-down-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 18:16:50 GMT</pubDate>
